CustomField.description: Field "Contractor Code" that has been set up on each "Purchasing Contract" in EAM. The Value will always be "MSN". This is used e.g. in the Subcontractors Claim process and is required as a column in the report/upload template in EAM.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Field "Contractor Code" on the "Purchasing Contract" in EAM. The Value is always "MSN".
CustomField.label: Contractor Code
